These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
There 4 different types of food: radish, avocado, pumpkin, kiwi
There are 4 different nationalities: italian, polish, indonesian, german
1. the polish is on the left of the italian##1
2. the person eating radish is the german##1
3. the indonesian is on the right of the italian##1
4. the person eating avocado is on the left of the german##1
5. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | kiwi | pumpkin | avocado | radish   |
| Nationality   | polish  | italian     | indonesian   | german |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, card-games, photography, baking
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, basketball, rugby, snowboarding
1. the person who's hobby is baking is the person who's sport is basketball##1
2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
4. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
5. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | photography | baking | card-games | sudoku    |
| Sport   | rugby    | basketball      | skiing | snowboarding |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, collecting, magic-tricks, skydiving
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, zombie, disaster, satire
1. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person watching spy movies##1
3. the person watching zombie movies is on the far right##1
4. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
5. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Hobby         | filmmaking | skydiving | magic-tricks   | collecting |
| Movie-Genre   | spy   | disaster | satire | zombie         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, mystery, romance, horror
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, volleyball, rowing, cycling
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person watching horror movies##1
2. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
3. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
4. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
5. the person who's sport is badminton is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | horror | mystery | adventure  | romance      |
| Sport         | volleyball | cycling   | rowing | badminton |

