.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-5::.
There 4 different types of food: lime, eggplant, radish, watermelon
4 different pets are kept: turtle, goat, guinea-pig, bird
1. the person eating eggplant is on the left of the person eating lime##1
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the person eating radish##1
3. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
4. the owner of the goat is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |  2   |    3     |      4      |
| Food   | watermelon | radish | eggplant | lime |
| Pet    | turtle       | bird | guinea-pig | goat     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-6::.
There are 4 different nationalities: indian, italian, egyptian, german
4 different pets are kept: hamster, rabbit, goat, ferret
1. the italian is on the far right##1
2. the german is on the left of the egyptian##1
3. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
4. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the egyptian##1
5. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Nationality   | german | egyptian | indian | italian |
| Pet           | hamster      | goat | ferret | rabbit    |

