.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, d&b, ambient, country
4 different pets are kept: frog, snake, rabbit, hamster
1. the owner of the rabbit is on the far left##1
2. the fan of country is on the far right##1
3. the fan of ambient is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the snake is on the far right##1
5. the fan of d&b is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |     3     |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | ambient | d&b | blues | country  |
| Pet           | rabbit | frog | hamster       | snake |

