.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-8::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, security-guard, dressmaker, software-developer
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, motorbike, subway, jet-ski
1. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the security-guard##1
2. the person driving the jet-ski is the software-developer##1
3. the security-guard is on the right of the dancer##1
4. the dressmaker is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
5. the person driving the scooter is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |    3     |    4     |
| Job         | dressmaker | dancer      | security-guard | software-developer |
| Transport   | scooter          | motorbike | subway     | jet-ski    |

