.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, tea, juice, iced-tea
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, jet-ski, airplane, van
1. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
2. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
3. the person driving the van is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
4. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |       3       |   4    |
| Beverage    | soy-milk | juice  | tea | iced-tea |
| Transport   | van | airplane | jet-ski          | subway    |

