.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, egyptian, german, british
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, roller, ship, helicopter
1. the person driving the tram is on the left of the egyptian##1
2. the person driving the roller is on the left of the british##1
3. the pakistani is on the left of the german##1
4. the british is the person driving the helicopter##1
5. the person driving the tram is on the left of the egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Nationality   | pakistani | german | egyptian | british   |
| Transport     | ship  | tram    | roller       | helicopter |

 